{"tid":1391982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇請我要攬炒巴打成立香港外交部","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:19:20.000Z","uid":171866,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73f3feb9ccae1357090ccf6ea127e6c15e2165c3","tid":1391982,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"而家香港有60幾個和平示威既年輕人將被重判暴動罪，面臨前所未有既政治打壓，相反白衣先輕判非法集結，其厚始薄彼既程度令人咋舌，更顯出法治已經被嚴重侵食，故有必須成立民間外交部，而攪炒巴經過幾次登報應該有一定代表性。而家美國打算通過《香港人權和民主法》證明美國非常重視香港人民主自由既情况<br />\n<br />\n故有需要向外大眾媒體登報直接反映本港人既聲音<br />\n<br />\n另外攬炒巴應該面對梗邊際效益既樽頸問題，應該要嘗試更多突破口"},{"pid":"7e62e452c05d7b0c5b883391199fc6ba41fe4442","tid":1391982,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=5f698d73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"a9cf0244fdc3f604dacfbf9cc3d421ed1b98e7d2","tid":1391982,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">陪審團行使否決權無需理由</code></pre>"},{"pid":"316c455d13c063942835d12487c5f1ae652fe24c","tid":1391982,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"建立一個有代表性嘅外交部"},{"pid":"747d72a49af1975b5ce7ac34be0348d348097d3b","tid":1391982,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316c455d13c063942835d12487c5f1ae652fe24c","tid":1391982,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"建立一個有代表性嘅外交部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:28:5